TITLE: Adding EF Core Instrumentation in Non-ASP.NET Core Applications
DESCRIPTION: Enables Entity Framework Core instrumentation in non-ASP.NET Core applications by passing EfCoreDiagnosticsSubscriber to the Agent.Subscribe method. This allows the agent to listen for diagnostic events from Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore 2.x+ and create database spans.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/apm-agent-dotnet/blob/main/docs/reference/setup-ef-core.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
