TITLE: Creating and Managing Child Spans in C#
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create and manage child spans, including proper exception handling and span termination.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/apm-agent-dotnet/blob/main/docs/reference/public-api.md#2025-04-22_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
ISpan childSpan = parentSpan.StartSpan("Select FROM customer",
     ApiConstants.TypeDb, ApiConstants.SubtypeMssql, ApiConstants.ActionQuery);
