TITLE: Mixing OpenTelemetry and Elastic APM Public API in C#
DESCRIPTION: Code example demonstrating how to use both the OpenTelemetry Activity API and Elastic APM Public API together. It creates a transaction with Elastic APM, then an OpenTelemetry span as a child, followed by another Elastic APM span as a child of the OpenTelemetry span.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/apm-agent-dotnet/blob/main/docs/reference/opentelemetry-bridge.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
/// ElasticTransaction
/// -
/// ---> OTelSpan
///           -
///           ---> ElasticSpan

var src = new ActivitySource("Test");
tracer.CaptureTransaction( nameof(Sample4), "test", t =>
{
	Thread.Sleep(100);
	using (var activity = src.StartActivity("foo"))
	{
		tracer.CurrentSpan.CaptureSpan("ElasticApmSpan", "test", () => Thread.Sleep(50));
		Thread.Sleep(150);
	}
});
```

