.Enrich.WithElasticApmCorrelationInfo()
.WriteTo.Elasticsearch(new ElasticsearchSinkOptions(new Uri("http://localhost:9200"))
{
  CustomFormatter = new EcsTextFormatter()
})
.CreateLogger();
```

