TITLE: Configuring BaggageToAttach in Elastic APM .NET Agent
DESCRIPTION: This configuration option controls which baggage values are automatically attached to events (transactions, spans, errors). It uses the W3C Baggage specification and can be programmatically accessed via the Activity API. The option supports dynamic configuration.
